OL,3,CMum with terminal cancer 'wastes' 14
OL,4,Cmonths applying for benefits
OL,6,FA mum with terminal bowel cancer who
OL,7,F"wasted months of precious time" with
OL,8,Fher family applying for benefits is
OL,9,Fcalling for the system to be
OL,10,Fsimplified.
OL,12,FBells, 56, spent 14 months going
OL,13,Fthrough appeals for Personal
OL,14,FIndependent Payments (PIP) as she was
OL,15,Funable to work during her cancer
OL,16,Ftreatment.
