OL,3,CMum with terminal cancer 'wastes' 14
OL,4,Cmonths applying for benefits
OL,6,FThe mum-of-two claims during her 90-
OL,7,Fminute interview a Department for Work
OL,8,Fand Pensions (DWP) medical assessor
OL,9,F"did not know where her bowel was"
OL,10,Fbefore rejecting her application.
OL,12,FShe said: "I expected help because I
OL,13,Fhave paid into the system all of my
OL,14,Flife. I've never lied. I've never
OL,15,Fcheated. I've never done anything
OL,16,Fwrong.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
