OL,3,CMum with terminal cancer 'wastes' 14
OL,4,Cmonths applying for benefits
OL,6,F"She asked me what my illness was and
OL,7,FI said bowel cancer. She said 'which
OL,8,Fpart of the body is that?' and I
OL,9,Fthought 'oh God.' They asked how far I
OL,10,Fcan walk in the length of a double
OL,11,Fdecker bus - it was ridiculous."
OL,13,FBells said with an uncertain future
OL,14,Fshe wanted to spend precious time with
OL,15,Ffamily and friends, but was forced to
OL,16,Fwaste months trying to navigate the
OL,17,Fcomplicated benefit paperwork
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
