OL,3,CMum with terminal cancer 'wastes' 14
OL,4,Cmonths applying for benefits
OL,6,F"It took me three gos to go through
OL,7,Fthe door. I chatted to the benefits
OL,8,Fgirls at Maggie's and you get a huge
OL,9,Fform in the post", she said.
OL,11,FWith the help of cancer charity
OL,12,FMaggie's and her local MP, Aphra
OL,13,FBrandreth, Bells, from Chester, is
OL,14,Fcalling for a special cancer benefit
OL,15,Fto simplify the process.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
