OL,3,CMum with terminal cancer 'wastes' 14
OL,4,Cmonths applying for benefits
OL,6,FThe Conservative MP for Chester South
OL,7,Fand Eddisbury said: "I want to see the
OL,8,Fright people getting help. There is
OL,9,Flimited money - we know that - but it
OL,10,Fdoesn't mean the system should be
OL,11,Fcompletely unfair."
OL,13,FBells said she was made to feel like
OL,14,Fshe was cheating the system, and says
OL,15,Fsimpler, bespoke benefits would make a
OL,16,Fworld of difference to families like
OL,17,Fhers.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
